e":"2017-08-18T17:13:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓豬幾時去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明晚去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />巴打你又去?</blockquote><br />\n我星期一 一齊玩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該未必得，因為今次係帶屋企人去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴打你會去邊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我台中同台北都會去啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 高美同梧棲觀光漁市 暫時諗唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n台中我都會去高美，之後會去下科學館/藝術館<br />\n仲有會去埔里玩飛行傘同清境農場<br />\n最後會去台南嘅奇美博物館</blockquote><br />\n有冇推薦地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你好熟台中？"},{"pid":"0717bc5d7b06293ffac52e07602669d59d9e7d6d","tid":359122,"uid":44930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T02:46:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓豬幾時去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明晚去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />巴打你又去?</blockquote><br />\n我星期一 一齊玩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該未必得，因為今次係帶屋企人去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴打你會去邊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我台中同台北都會去啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 高美同梧棲觀光漁市 暫時諗唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n台中我都會去高美，之後會去下科學館/藝術館<br />\n仲有會去埔里玩飛行傘同清境農場<br />\n最後會去台南嘅奇美博物館</blockquote><br />\n有冇推薦地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你好熟台中？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可以去北屯區嘅大坑紙箱王(裏面有大大小小嘅用紙製造嘅藝術品，台中內有好多間分店，但呢間係最大最多嘢睇)， 附近仲有心之芳庭，鍾意影相嘅可以去睇睇<br />\n<br />\n仲有新社嘅新社莊園同埋薰衣草森林， 鍾意食菇可以順便去埋百菇莊，如果係嗰度會食埋dinner嘅話可以去菇神嗰度一邊食嘢一邊睇黃昏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔熟悉台中，我妹妹熟悉佢去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n非台中地帶嘅話如果你仲未訂好酒店可以去清境嗰度居住一兩日<br />\n嗰度清境農場都唔錯，仲可以預一日清晨去合歡山睇日出同雲海(去之前報當地團)"}]}